{"type": "article", "id": 9888, "title": "BASE 桌面用品", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-22T07:26:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235607jCVT42oYdinEF9ht.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自旧金山的设计工作室 BASE 推出了一个桌面用品系列，意在提升桌面的整洁度，从而提升工作效率。这个系列包括各种型号的收纳盒，笔筒和烟灰缸等，皆采用 3D 打印形成。材料上选用的聚苯乙烯，配色上所有产品选用整洁的白色，黑色，灰色和橘红色，轮廓简单温柔。产品价格在 35 美元左右，<a href=\"http://base-object.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235605rOmxB0F7NyR84Ech.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235605DXQnIyZ4YACBJaWG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235605xjXFk9sdCDZJ8Hqn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235606CivNredF1t2IQHVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}